data.title: JAZZ ORKESTAR HRT-A (2017)
data.meta_description: motion picture |   Made-for-TV series.   Feature film (over 60 minutes).   1. "The rewrite of spring", "Folk song No. 1", "Thirds of April", "New skies", "Charlottenville" by Lars Møller. (Songs).   1. Croatian RadioTelevision Jazz Orchestra (inc: Miru Kadoica, as), Lars Møller, tenor sax, music director. (Personnel On Camera).   1. Recorded on 8th June 2017 in Muzej Suvremene Umjetnosti, Zagreb.
